summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Thirteen Thousand Six Hundred Fifty-seven & 62/100 ($13,657.62) Dollars, or so much thereof as may be necessary to pay the city's portion of the cost of the improvement of Roy Street, and West Roy Street, et al, by paving, as provided for in Ordinance No. 18311, creating Local Improvement District No. 1726.
